1
00:00:17,763 --> 00:00:19,498
[groan]

2
00:00:24,304 --> 00:00:27,408
Huh?

3
00:00:29,176 --> 00:00:30,544
Naruto!

4
00:00:30,578 --> 00:00:32,112
[grunt]

5
00:00:32,146 --> 00:00:34,784
[gasps]

6
00:00:34,816 --> 00:00:36,918
Yes!  You have regained
consciousness!

7
00:00:36,951 --> 00:00:38,487
{\an1}Oh, thank goodness!

8
00:00:38,521 --> 00:00:39,922
Where am I?

9
00:00:39,955 --> 00:00:43,025
{\an1}Is everyone okay?

10
00:00:43,059 --> 00:00:46,129
{\an1}We were all about to head
back to the village.

11
00:00:46,163 --> 00:00:48,832
{\an1}For some reason, the
enemy has retreated.

12
00:00:48,865 --> 00:00:52,103
{\an1}Yeah. Even though we
were at a disadvantage...

13
00:00:52,136 --> 00:00:55,507
{\an1}We think their goal was to
deliver Sasuke to Orochimaru.

14
00:00:55,541 --> 00:00:59,845
Although, that's really
little more than a hunch.

15
00:00:59,878 --> 00:01:03,818
{\an1}Uh...  But where's Sasuke?  What
happened to Sasuke, guys?!

16
00:01:03,850 --> 00:01:08,222
{\an1}When I finally caught up with
you, the only thing I found
was you, unconscious.

17
00:01:08,255 --> 00:01:09,458
[grunt]

18
00:01:09,491 --> 00:01:13,061
{\an1}I'm sorry, but... we couldn't
track them due to the rain.

19
00:01:14,630 --> 00:01:16,800
Oh, I see...

20
00:01:16,834 --> 00:01:18,134
[grunt]

21
00:01:24,342 --> 00:01:28,913
{\an1}Yeah, but... I promised Sakura
that I'd bring Sasuke back...

22
00:01:28,947 --> 00:01:30,583
[grunt]

23
00:01:30,616 --> 00:01:32,585
{\an1}Hey, just take it easy!

24
00:01:32,618 --> 00:01:36,021
{\an1}No way! I mean, I can't just sit
around here doing nothing, you
know!

25
00:01:36,056 --> 00:01:38,693
{\an1}[crows squawking]

26
00:01:41,462 --> 00:01:44,198
Huh...

27
00:01:45,534 --> 00:01:55,513
<i>♪</i>

28
00:01:55,546 --> 00:02:05,591
<i>♪</i>

29
00:02:05,591 --> 00:02:15,603
<i>♪</i>

30
00:03:29,691 --> 00:03:33,262
{\an1}I've sent Kotetsu
and Izumo home.

31
00:03:33,295 --> 00:03:36,733
{\an1}But just to be safe,... Kakashi
is going to stay overnight.

32
00:03:36,766 --> 00:03:40,604
{\an1}Yes, I understand.
Well, that's a relief.

33
00:03:40,638 --> 00:03:42,874
Urgent news!

34
00:03:42,908 --> 00:03:45,343
{\an1}Someone has just managed to
infiltrate the village!

35
00:03:46,645 --> 00:03:48,179
[gasp]

36
00:03:58,659 --> 00:04:00,929
You are...

37
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:05,066
{\an1}It's been a long time,
Lady Tsunade...

38
00:04:05,099 --> 00:04:07,169
{\an1}Do you know him?

39
00:04:07,202 --> 00:04:11,775
{\an1}Wait, you're that boy from long
ago that Jiraiya saved, the one
from the Hidden Rain.

40
00:04:11,808 --> 00:04:13,209
<i>Yahiko, right?</i>

41
00:04:13,243 --> 00:04:17,682
It seems you do
remember me, then...

42
00:04:17,715 --> 00:04:20,284
{\an1}However, I'm now known as Pain.

43
00:04:20,318 --> 00:04:24,523
{\an1}Yahiko?! The one from
the Hizashi incident
three years ago?!

44
00:04:24,556 --> 00:04:26,960
{\an1}So why did you sneak
into our village now?

45
00:04:26,993 --> 00:04:28,695
{\an1}Our pain is twofold.  First...

46
00:04:28,728 --> 00:04:31,899
{\an1}...from the Five Great
Nations...

47
00:04:31,932 --> 00:04:34,535
{\an1}...and the Five Great
Villages...

48
00:04:34,568 --> 00:04:39,240
{\an1}The pain of being trampled...the
pain of all the people that you
killed.

49
00:04:39,274 --> 00:04:47,283
{\an1}And secondly,  the pain in our
hearts caused by the Leaf's
betrayal.

50
00:04:47,316 --> 00:04:51,121
{\an1}<i>...Our pain... will become</i>
<i>the whole world's pain!</i>

51
00:04:51,154 --> 00:04:53,725
No...

52
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:04,337
{\an1}True Planetary Devastation!

53
00:05:09,443 --> 00:05:15,384
{\an1}[loud engulfing noise]

54
00:05:27,331 --> 00:05:28,967
[grunt]

55
00:06:01,005 --> 00:06:02,707
[gasp]

56
00:06:25,801 --> 00:06:29,973
{\an1}What is that thing?!

57
00:06:31,273 --> 00:06:34,145
{\an1}Shikamaru! Explain
what's going on here!

58
00:06:34,178 --> 00:06:41,153
{\an1}Well, as you can see... this is
something ^ that seems to defy
explanation-and reality...

59
00:06:41,186 --> 00:06:44,490
{\an1}Hey, Neji! Is everyone in
the village still safe?

60
00:06:44,523 --> 00:06:48,027
{\an1}I mean, can you confirm what's
inside that big thing with your
Byakugan?

61
00:06:48,061 --> 00:06:55,736
{\an1}Of course. I'm on it now.

62
00:06:55,770 --> 00:07:00,375
{\an1}I can see chakra, and it seems
to be coming from the villagers.

63
00:07:00,408 --> 00:07:02,444
{\an1}So they're okay
inside there?!

64
00:07:02,477 --> 00:07:06,150
{\an1}It appears so, but I'm not
entirely positive.

65
00:07:06,183 --> 00:07:08,418
[grunt]

66
00:07:09,686 --> 00:07:10,788
{\an1}Naruto!

67
00:07:10,821 --> 00:07:13,323
{\an1}What do you think you're doing?!
In your condition?!

68
00:07:13,357 --> 00:07:16,929
{\an1}I don't know what kind of jutsu
that is, but I'm gonna undo it
right now!

69
00:07:16,962 --> 00:07:18,464
Huh?

70
00:07:19,431 --> 00:07:22,169
{\an1}Hey, Sakura...! I'm
glad you're okay!

71
00:07:22,202 --> 00:07:23,970
{\an1}I was out on a mission,
and I just got back.

72
00:07:24,004 --> 00:07:26,874
{\an1}But what's going on here?  What
happened to the village?

73
00:07:26,908 --> 00:07:29,610
{\an1}We don't know! We just
got back here, too.

74
00:07:29,644 --> 00:07:32,714
{\an1}But we have to find the guy who
did this and rescue everyone!

75
00:07:32,748 --> 00:07:33,949
{\an1}So, let's do this!

76
00:07:33,982 --> 00:07:36,186
{\an1}That's crazy!  You shouldn't
even move in your condition!

77
00:07:36,219 --> 00:07:39,522
{\an1}Everyone in the village is
inside of that thing!

78
00:07:39,556 --> 00:07:42,525
{\an1}We can't just sit around down
here and twiddle our thumbs!

79
00:07:42,559 --> 00:07:45,663
{\an1}[gasp]... All right, kneel down!

80
00:07:45,696 --> 00:07:46,664
Huh?!

81
00:07:46,697 --> 00:07:48,200
{\an1}C'mon!  Just kneel down!

82
00:07:50,569 --> 00:07:52,872
{\an1}You need to recover first.

83
00:07:53,239 --> 00:07:55,107
Oh, right.

84
00:07:57,510 --> 00:08:02,716
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Okay... I'll use this time to...</i>

85
00:08:12,061 --> 00:08:15,332
{\an1}What's this?! What's
happening here?

86
00:08:15,364 --> 00:08:20,403
{\an1}Seems the power supply was
cut, and the emergency
back-up system was activated.

87
00:08:28,314 --> 00:08:30,549
{\an8}I can't teleport
outside the village?

88
00:08:34,754 --> 00:08:38,826
{\an1}The wall... is it closing in?!

89
00:08:39,327 --> 00:08:42,931
{\an1}At this rate-- A simple
Earth Style will do!

90
00:08:43,199 --> 00:08:46,736
{\an1}<i>Use a rock pillar as a support</i>
<i>to stop it from closing in</i>
<i>further!</i>

91
00:08:46,769 --> 00:08:52,242
{\an1}<i>The Akimichi Clan will use their</i>
<i>Super Expansion Jutsu to push</i>
<i>the wall back!</i>

92
00:08:59,351 --> 00:09:03,255
[yell]

93
00:09:13,567 --> 00:09:18,473
[grunts]
I'll do whatever it takes
to hold it back!

94
00:09:19,342 --> 00:09:25,815
{\an1}Leaf Police Force!  Our priority
is to keep the villagers safe!

95
00:09:25,848 --> 00:09:27,517
Now, go!

96
00:09:32,123 --> 00:09:38,064
{\an1}We will protect the Hidden Leaf
Village! We will stop this wall,
no matter what it takes!

97
00:09:39,065 --> 00:09:42,735
{\an1}[charging up yell]

98
00:09:46,773 --> 00:09:50,678
{\an1}Physical attacks don't
have any effect at all!

99
00:09:57,053 --> 00:10:01,658
<i>[explosions]</i>

100
00:10:05,363 --> 00:10:08,733
{\an1}Everyone has reacted swiftly
and jumped in to help!

101
00:10:10,268 --> 00:10:14,573
{\an1}Minato! This is a special
Sealing Jutsu!

102
00:10:14,606 --> 00:10:18,511
{\an1}If this keeps up, everyone'll
be crushed by the mass of
stone around us, ya know!!

103
00:10:18,544 --> 00:10:23,284
{\an1}Everyone is pushing it back.
But you're right, it's only
a matter of time...

104
00:10:23,817 --> 00:10:27,289
{\an1}We have to figure out
what we can to do about
the jutsu caster...

105
00:10:27,323 --> 00:10:28,424
{\an1}<i>(Kushina thought)</i>
<i>Lord Fourth!</i>

106
00:10:28,457 --> 00:10:29,458
[gasp]

107
00:10:29,492 --> 00:10:30,760
Huh?

108
00:10:32,429 --> 00:10:37,402
{\an1}I have an idea to try. Kushina,
please stay here with these two
for right now, okay?

109
00:10:38,835 --> 00:10:41,439
{\an1}Flying Raijin Jutsu!

110
00:10:50,283 --> 00:10:52,218
Lord Third, sir!

111
00:10:52,252 --> 00:10:53,686
{\an1}Yes, Minato?

112
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:56,190
{\an1}We think this is a sealing
attack by the enemy.

113
00:10:56,223 --> 00:11:00,728
{\an1}And unless this jutsu... is
countered with another
jutsu of equal strength...

114
00:11:00,761 --> 00:11:03,031
{\an1}...everyone inside
here will be crushed.

115
00:11:03,065 --> 00:11:05,368
{\an1}Just as I suspected...

116
00:11:05,401 --> 00:11:08,738
{\an1}I was thinking that we could
try using the Four Crimson
Ray Formation.

117
00:11:08,771 --> 00:11:11,341
{\an1}But I'm going to need your help
to do that, Lord Hiruzen...

118
00:11:11,375 --> 00:11:14,111
{\an1}Right. Yes, let's try it.

119
00:11:19,751 --> 00:11:24,391
{\an1}Wait, Lord Fourth, I
know Tsunade has power
equal to a Hokage

120
00:11:24,424 --> 00:11:25,758
{\an1}But that's only three of us.

121
00:11:25,791 --> 00:11:29,262
{\an1}The Four Crimson Ray
Formation requires four people.

122
00:11:29,296 --> 00:11:32,166
{\an1}Kushina also possesses
the Nine Tails' chakra.

123
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:36,438
{\an1}And she has far more experience
with Sealing Jutsu than anyone
else here right now...

124
00:11:36,472 --> 00:11:38,807
{\an1}Rivaling even that of a Hokage.

125
00:11:38,841 --> 00:11:43,780
{\an1}Yeah, but this Sealing Jutsu is
too strong for the Four Crimson
Ray Formation!

126
00:11:43,813 --> 00:11:49,019
{\an4}I mean, even a Tailed Beast
would have a really difficult
time trying to suppress it, ya
know.

127
00:11:50,988 --> 00:11:52,557
[explosion]

128
00:11:52,591 --> 00:11:54,926
{\an1}There's no time left!

129
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:59,765
{\an4}If we combine our strength with
everyone who's pushing back
against the wall, at least we
might be able to buy some time!

130
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:01,834
{\an1}So we buy time, but then what?

131
00:12:01,868 --> 00:12:04,471
{\an1}Unless we can stop the jutsu,
this solves nothing!

132
00:12:04,505 --> 00:12:06,940
{\an1}We'll think of something
definitive in that time!

133
00:12:06,974 --> 00:12:08,877
{\an1}Please get to the
village's four corners.

134
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:10,613
[groan] All right.

135
00:12:10,645 --> 00:12:15,217
{\an1}Shizune,  your job now is to
tend to the wounded!

136
00:12:15,251 --> 00:12:16,453
Understood.

137
00:12:18,455 --> 00:12:23,026
{\an1}<i>[crumbling and cracking]</i>

138
00:12:27,131 --> 00:12:30,869
{\an1}Four Crimson Ray Formation!

139
00:12:51,127 --> 00:12:53,129
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>All right, everyone,</i>
<i>hang in there...</i>

140
00:12:53,162 --> 00:12:56,066
{\an1}<i>If we can buy some time,</i>
<i>there's still hope.</i>

141
00:13:12,653 --> 00:13:15,021
[exhale]

142
00:13:17,024 --> 00:13:21,129
{\an1}Awesome, Sakura!  Thanks to you,
I think I'm fully recovered now!

143
00:13:22,864 --> 00:13:24,667
[gasp]

144
00:13:26,903 --> 00:13:29,105
Why, that...!

145
00:13:29,339 --> 00:13:32,176
{\an1}Hey, wait, Naruto! Don't
rush in like that!

146
00:13:32,209 --> 00:13:34,211
{\an1}You just recovered a second ago!

147
00:13:34,245 --> 00:13:36,747
{\an1}This kid is just hopeless...

148
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:38,550
Summoning Jutsu!

149
00:13:44,625 --> 00:13:48,862
{\an1}So, was it you guys? Are you the
ones who wrecked the village?!

150
00:13:50,632 --> 00:13:52,433
[attack yell]

151
00:13:55,803 --> 00:14:00,943
{\an1}First of all, I'm gonna beat up
every last one of you guys

152
00:14:00,976 --> 00:14:02,712
{\an1}and then we're gonna talk!

153
00:14:05,483 --> 00:14:06,983
{\an1}That guy is...!

154
00:14:07,017 --> 00:14:09,887
{\an1}Naruto! That guy's Yahiko!

155
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:11,889
{\an1}He was a part of Team Jiraiya.

156
00:14:11,922 --> 00:14:14,192
{\an1}Wait, you destroyed
that village back then!

157
00:14:14,226 --> 00:14:16,862
{\an1}You say you're Pervy
Sage's students?!

158
00:14:16,895 --> 00:14:20,533
We're the Akatsuki.
And I'm Tendo Pain.

159
00:14:20,567 --> 00:14:22,336
What...

160
00:14:22,369 --> 00:14:26,974
{\an1}We cast off the name Jiraiya the
moment the Hokage of the Hidden
Leaf burned that village

161
00:14:27,007 --> 00:14:28,243
{\an1}and everything inside
of it to the ground...

162
00:14:28,276 --> 00:14:32,615
{\an1}...just to hide the
embarrassment that
occurred there.

163
00:14:32,648 --> 00:14:37,320
{\an1}What are you talking about?  You
were the ones who destroyed that
entire village!

164
00:14:37,688 --> 00:14:41,825
We have proof. And now,
to render judgment...

165
00:14:41,858 --> 00:14:44,996
...for the pain
caused to the weak.

166
00:14:46,699 --> 00:14:54,240
{\an1}The pain of death... the pain of
my friends... my precious
friends...

167
00:14:54,274 --> 00:15:00,281
{\an1}The Hokage and the people of the
Hidden Leaf Village... will get
to taste pain!

168
00:15:03,317 --> 00:15:05,554
{\an1}I'll settle this right now!

169
00:15:07,889 --> 00:15:09,726
<i>[explosion]</i>

170
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:11,461
[gasps]

171
00:15:11,494 --> 00:15:14,931
[wince] Naruto!

172
00:15:23,576 --> 00:15:25,711
Summoning Jutsu!

173
00:15:27,146 --> 00:15:28,381
Naruto...!

174
00:15:28,414 --> 00:15:30,484
{\an1}[Gasp] What are you doing?!

175
00:15:30,517 --> 00:15:34,655
{\an1}You can't! That Pain guy isn't
an opponent we can deal with.

176
00:15:34,689 --> 00:15:38,559
{\an1}Naruto, however...

177
00:15:50,374 --> 00:15:52,576
That's amazing.

178
00:15:52,610 --> 00:15:54,345
Summoning Jutsu!

179
00:15:56,981 --> 00:15:59,151
{\an1}Shadow Clone Jutsu!

180
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:08,897
{\an1}Sage Art: Giant Rasengan!

181
00:16:08,929 --> 00:16:11,231
{\an1}You're right. It's a
different level...

182
00:16:11,265 --> 00:16:14,302
{\an1}But still, I cannot just
stand here watching this!

183
00:16:14,335 --> 00:16:17,005
{\an1}If we get a chance,
we must assist him!

184
00:16:18,307 --> 00:16:20,409
[grunt]

185
00:16:20,443 --> 00:16:27,618
{\an1}I see... That's Sage Jutsu.
So you've mastered the same
jutsu as Jiraiya Sensei.

186
00:16:27,652 --> 00:16:30,722
{\an1}You're no student of Pervy
Sage's, not with what you
guys are doing!

187
00:16:30,756 --> 00:16:34,726
{\an1}Now I'm gonna pulverize you!
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

188
00:16:38,531 --> 00:16:42,403
{\an1}Sage Art: Rasen Shuriken!

189
00:17:00,491 --> 00:17:04,629
{\an1}[panting breaths]

190
00:17:04,662 --> 00:17:13,072
{\an1}As I suspected... Sage Mode lasts
no more than five minutes...

191
00:17:15,509 --> 00:17:17,544
What's this?!

192
00:17:17,577 --> 00:17:19,514
Universal Pull.

193
00:17:19,881 --> 00:17:22,216
[gasp] Argh!

194
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:23,652
[gasps]

195
00:17:29,726 --> 00:17:33,563
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>He's sucking all the Sage Jutsu</i>
<i>chakra right out of me!</i>

196
00:17:33,597 --> 00:17:35,966
{\an1}<i>This'll be just perfect...!</i>

197
00:17:48,949 --> 00:17:52,887
[grunt]

198
00:17:58,459 --> 00:18:00,161
[cry of pain]

199
00:18:00,629 --> 00:18:03,699
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>What was that?  Is someone</i>
<i>watching? </i>

200
00:18:03,732 --> 00:18:09,139
{\an1}So tell me, has this tamed you,
my sibling student...?

201
00:18:09,172 --> 00:18:11,809
{\an1}Naruto! I am coming
to help you!

202
00:18:11,842 --> 00:18:14,145
Almighty Push!

203
00:18:14,178 --> 00:18:15,647
Arghhh!

204
00:18:16,380 --> 00:18:17,783
{\an1}Lee!

205
00:18:18,216 --> 00:18:19,384
[gasp]

206
00:18:22,355 --> 00:18:23,656
[gasp]

207
00:18:26,894 --> 00:18:29,030
{\an1}I won't let you hurt Naruto
anymore!

208
00:18:29,965 --> 00:18:33,068
{\an1}That's right!  Hinata was on a
mission outside the village!

209
00:18:33,100 --> 00:18:35,972
Why did you come
out here?! Just run!

210
00:18:36,005 --> 00:18:37,940
You can't win!

211
00:18:38,374 --> 00:18:43,680
{\an1}I'm not afraid to die right
here... if it means I can
protect you!

212
00:18:43,714 --> 00:18:46,651
{\an1}And that's because Naruto is my-

213
00:18:46,684 --> 00:18:48,886
<i>(Tendo Pain)</i>
<i>Almighty Push!</i>

214
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:51,890
[screams]

215
00:18:52,357 --> 00:18:56,029
<i>(Tendo Pain)</i>
<i>I've experienced it countless</i>
<i>times, right before my eyes, </i>

216
00:18:56,062 --> 00:18:58,632
{\an1}<i>so close I could feel</i>
<i>their breath...</i>

217
00:18:58,665 --> 00:19:01,468
{\an1}...people dear to me dying...

218
00:19:01,501 --> 00:19:04,672
Share my pain!

219
00:19:10,113 --> 00:19:12,214
{\an1}Yes, it was just like this...

220
00:19:12,247 --> 00:19:16,954
